OL,3,CTrain driver completes final journey
OL,4,Cto end 50-year railway career
OL,6,FA train driver has been greeted with
OL,7,Fcheers as he pulled into London for
OL,8,Fthe final time - completing his 50-
OL,9,Fyear career on the railways.
OL,11,FGirish Jani, 67, took to the controls
OL,12,Fof an Avanti West Coast train from
OL,13,FCrewe to London Euston for his last
OL,14,Ftask before retirement.
OL,16,FHe joined the industry as a 17-year-
OL,17,Fold in September 1974, starting as a
OL,18,Ftrain driver's assistant at a freight
OL,19,Fdepot in Wembley, north-west London,
OL,20,Fbefore later becoming a driver.
