OL,6,FMr Jani went to be a deputy team
OL,7,Fmanager and also trained and assessed
OL,8,Fthe next generation of drivers.
OL,10,FThe "valuable leader" was greeted with
OL,11,Fcheers and applause at Euston on
OL,12,FSeptember 20 as colleagues from his
OL,13,Fentire career gathered to celebrate
OL,14,Fthe occasion.
OL,16,FIn a statement, Mr Jani said: "I feel
OL,17,Ftruly proud and privileged to have
OL,18,Fclocked up 50 years' service.
OL,20,F"It only feels like yesterday I
OL,21,Fstarted on my railway journey.
