OL,6,F"I will miss the people, driving
OL,7,Ftrains and playing my part in
OL,8,Fsupporting the next generation of
OL,9,Ftrain drivers ` I look forward to
OL,10,Ftravelling on their trains one day.
OL,12,F"I'm excited to start a new chapter
OL,13,Fwhere I'll get to look at my bucket
OL,14,Flist for travel, continue my
OL,15,Fmagistrate duties and spend quality
OL,16,Ftime with my family."
