OL,4,Cto end 50-year railway career
OL,6,FThe 67-year-old has also been a
OL,7,Fmagistrate in London for 18 years,
OL,8,Fbelieving the role requires similar
OL,9,Fskills to driving a train, such as
OL,10,Ftaking on responsibility, having
OL,11,Fattention to detail and good
OL,12,Fcommunication.
OL,14,FTransport work is part of Mr Jani's
OL,15,Ffamily, as he followed in the
OL,16,Ffootsteps of his brothers, with one
OL,17,Fworking as a train driver at London
OL,18,FUnderground for over 35 years, while
OL,19,Fthe other worked for British Rail for
OL,20,F22 years.
