OL,6,FAvanti West Coast deputy head of
OL,7,Fdrivers Craig Fletcher said: "Working
OL,8,Fwith Jani was invaluable when I joined
OL,9,FEuston depot.
OL,11,F"Jani's relations and the connections
OL,12,Fhe built with people over the years is
OL,13,Ftestament to his personable approach.
OL,15,F"He has a unique charisma and charm `
OL,16,Fsometimes playfully cheeky ` that
OL,17,Fmakes him memorable and a valuable
OL,18,Fleader."
